Note: ===================================================================
Note: LATEX SEMANTIC ANALYZER
Note: ===================================================================
Note: Semantic analysis for LaTeX document preparation system. Handles
Note: document structure validation, package compatibility, reference
Note: resolution, citation validation, and academic document best practices.

Note: Part of the Translation System
Note: Location: compiler/middle/gungnir/hir/translation/frontends/latex/latex_semantic.runa
Note: ===================================================================

