Process called "latex_semantic_analyze" takes latex_ast as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Perform semantic analysis on LaTeX AST

    Let analyzer be proc create_latex_semantic_analyzer
    If analyzer is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If

    Let result be proc analyze_latex_document with analyzer, latex_ast
    Return analyzer
End Process

